{"tid":410391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何君堯呢？】訛稱前港隊高價招生 羽球教練判社服","createTime":"2017-09-23T01:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T07:21:45.000Z","uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"543d51ee78e6c8900ede32565e18df1d7718a20b","tid":410391,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170531/s00001/1496205657388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170531%2Fs00001%2F1496205657388&d=suILLRUCbb1r6ajeQm%2F9vozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7ee73c58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170531%2Fs00001%2F1496205657388&h=d927e67a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170531/s00001/1496205657388</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】羽毛球教練宣傳招生時訛稱是香港代表隊前成員、曾代表香港參加亞運，收取較一般教練貴1倍的學費。羽毛球教練早前承認一項「要約提供已應用虛假商品說明的服務」罪，昨被判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n官：給被告最後機會<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時稱，今次給予被告梁浚豪（27歲，圓圖）最後一次機會，是由於他的確有參與羽毛球運動和比賽，且有悔意，故接納感化官建議判處社服令。控方案情指海關於去年2月接到投訴，指被告在一個球會的社交網站、卡片和海報上訛稱是港隊成員。海關向香港羽毛球總會查詢，會方指被告從來不是港隊成員，僅10多年前參加過該會的「重點青年軍訓練計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n海關其後「放蛇」相約被告於4月13日到球場上羽毛球班，被告當日再自稱是港隊成員和參加過亞運，而他收取的學費為每小時450元。由於被告違反《商品說明條例》，海關將他拘捕。根據資料，一般註冊教練收費約每堂每小時200至300元。<br />\n<br />\n平民百姓老吹就差啲要食皇家飯，何君堯老吹有英國律師執業資格係咪有大紫荊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eed9399635ff72ee33139ab08e5c98efbfefdd4","tid":410391,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e756e43ac6c0fa6ccafc47bf522ff7059a4d3e","tid":410391,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:15:09.000Z","msg":"法律界人士最叻就係引用案例<br />\n呢單嘢何妖唔係甩到身啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4bde7dc7ce76adc603c6e5cc9bb1187b887afc","tid":410391,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"袁國強： 唔能夠睇一兩個字, 要睇背景<br />\n<br />\n(乜背景? 黑社會背景定共產黨背景?)"},{"pid":"c5da2cc1f7ab64aeb0d1b0cae6c5c9ac9d368616","tid":410391,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:44:13.000Z","msg":"執葉的背景，當然是英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd372282fb0214def076398b64270801ac5066a","tid":410391,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"唔知呃選票要判幾耐呢"},{"pid":"db4702b8331600545c5afd2e74d603c8a1a9fe28","tid":410391,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ec394a1a69844dfc09557ddea07fd9f27a5c57","tid":410391,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"宜加何君堯涉嫌冒認英國同新加坡執業律師<br />\n起碼要坐番13個月啩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}